{"tid":957787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6歲泰國龍鳳胎結婚 父母︰不結婚會行衰運","createTime":"2018-12-27T09:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T08:19:07.000Z","uid":150685,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78722e3288f51a09f3ee9e862e1a7e894d3b02b6","tid":957787,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:50:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">泰國有一對6歲的龍鳳胎在家人安排下結婚，兩名孩子的父母相信他們上輩子是情人，只有盡快結婚才能避免將來遭遇厄運</span>，於是上周一為他們安排了華麗婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n小新郎「Guitar」及小新娘「Kiwi」在2012年9月出生，他們的父母為兩人在曼谷郊外北欖府（Samut Prakan）安排婚禮，有多名親友及鄰居出席。雖然是自家人，但娶新娘當然要付禮金，「Guitar」要準備20萬泰銖（5萬港元）現金和價值1,000英鎊（9,900港元）黃金迎娶「Kiwi」，新郎還要按傳統儀式在街上巡遊，通過9道「門」才可以見到新娘。<br />\n<br />\n泰國佛教徒相信「因果報應」，認為龍鳳胎是前世的戀人，由於兩人上輩子的「債」未還清，所以今生以龍鳳胎身份一起出生，如果他們不盡快結婚，就會在未來遭遇厄運。不過，事實上這場婚禮並沒有法律效力，他們長大後照樣可以另尋各自的伴侶。<br />\n<br />\n父親瑪利拉德（Malirat）說：「辦這場婚禮儀式是因為我們相信兩名小孩前世是情人，這種信仰是由古人傳下來的。我們必須為一對雙胞胎安排婚禮，去處理兩人前世遺留下來的問題。如果他們結了婚，他們會健康、成功地生活，也不會生病」。<br />\n<br />\n母親帕差拉博爾恩（Phacharaporn）稱一對子女在婚禮時非常「甜蜜」，「他們會互相成為生命中的好友，當他們長大後，可以各自找到自己的丈夫及妻子，但這場婚禮對他們來說很重要。」<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181227/59071185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181227%2F59071185&d=idkdSC%2BxPlwqqHT1giX9GhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=f7900431\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181227%2F59071185&h=11cb8827\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181227/59071185</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5047a80e24637befabe95ccdd99c9313211a10a","tid":957787,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:51:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d5c49a444cc1dda00faf6262ace52673de6189f","tid":957787,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"雖然是自家人，但娶新娘當然要付禮金<br />\n<br />\n左手交右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38639afd01c0fb5c2c8819ebde57f809d6fbcb57","tid":957787,"uid":91771,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3d5c49a444cc1dda00faf6262ace52673de6189f","tid":957787,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"雖然是自家人，但娶新娘當然要付禮金<br />\n<br />\n左手交右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:57:38.000Z","msg":"諗起自己封利是比自己篇潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a40f629ff37869818daad10dc9ff4fc8c65fed","tid":957787,"uid":225295,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"兩名孩子的父母相信他們上輩子是情人<br />\n<br />\n同d咩女兒係老豆上世情人一樣咁戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74351b8822d1d2e77f1673a4cb43b198d092996f","tid":957787,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:19:07.000Z","msg":"「他們會互相成為生命中的好友，當他們長大後，可以各自找到自己的丈夫及妻子，但這場婚禮對他們來說很重要。」<br />\n<br />\njm9"}]}